## Broadcast Template

### General Template

```text
[中文] 完成：<what was done, current status>。我的判断：<trade-offs and assumptions, or "严格按需求">。需要你看：<review points>。风险：<if any>。 | [EN] Done: <what, current status>. My calls: <tradeoffs, or "followed spec strictly">. Review: <check points>. Risk: <if any>.
```

### Example: Normal Completion

```text
[中文] 完成：用户导出功能支持 CSV 和 Excel 两种格式，改了 ExportService.ts 和 FileUtils.ts，可以正常运行。我的判断：严格按需求，两种格式都做了。需要你看：导出大数据量时的性能表现。 | [EN] Done: User export supports CSV and Excel formats, modified ExportService.ts and FileUtils.ts, runs correctly. My calls: followed spec strictly. Review: performance with large datasets.
```

### Example: With Trade-offs

```text
[中文] 完成：搜索结果分页功能，改了 SearchController.ts。我的判断：分页用了游标方式而不是 offset，因为大数据量下性能更好，你看看合不合适。需要你看：翻页交互和排序是否符合预期。 | [EN] Done: Search result pagination, modified SearchController.ts. My calls: used cursor-based instead of offset pagination for better large-dataset performance — please check if that works for you. Review: paging UX and sort order.
```

